column1: #Text=Thissling , statistician for the Traralgon Football Club senior side
#Text=Wikinews contributor Patrick Gillett interviewed Andy Thissling of the Traralgon Football Club .
#Text=Andy is the statistician for the Gippsland Football League clubs senior side , or first XVIII .

#Text=The Gippsland Football League ( officially Gippsland League , GL ) is the only major Australian rules football competition in the Gippsland region according to the Victorian Country Football League .
#Text=: Can you describe what you do at Traraglon footy club ?
#Text=On match day , I do the stats for the Traralgon Football Club , for the seniors .
#Text=I want to have this job for ever .
#Text=How Long have you been doing this ?
#Text=How long have I been doing the stats for ?
#Text=I got asked to do it and since then , I 've been doing since 2004 to today 's date .
#Text=How often do you talk to the coach and provide him with the stats ?
#Text=Each quarter I go to the coaching staff and get them all my stats to them and tell it to them what 's what .
#Text=An the I do them at the end of the quarter .
#Text=And then at the end of the game I 'll hand them my stats .
#Text=A South Australian store is pictured here
#Text=What is your job out side of football ?
#Text=My job outside of football is , I work at a supermarket called Coles Supermarket in Traralgon .
#Text=I work there three days a week .
#Text=That keeps me out of mischief for a few days .
#Text=Traralgon won the 2009 minor premiership , equivalent to the premiership in association football , but failed to win the premiership , equivalent to the championship
#Text=Does working at Coles effect your involvement with the footy club ?
#Text=It 's just three days of work and that 's all .
#Text=The rest I 'll stay home do some house work and get ready for footy on Saturdays .
#Text=Will Traralgon win the minor premiership this year , like they did last year ?
#Text=We take one game at a time and that 's all .
#Text=Damn straight it is , Good to hear .
#Text=Has there ever been a point when you 've wanted to give up doing the stats ?
#Text=I just like to do it and if I want a break it give someone else a go and tell then the action .
#Text=Final question - do you want to add anything for readers ?
#Text=Thanks for you time Pat and keep up the good work mate .
